# PATCH: 0027-inventory-filter-diff-export
# WHY: Inventory dễ audit hơn: (A) lọc service/task Microsoft (mặc định ẩn, checkbox hiện lại +
#      checkbox chỉ hiện service Running); (B) so sánh 2 lần quét (software mới/gỡ, service đổi state);
#      (C) export CSV/JSON toàn fleet.
# WHAT: collect-inventory.ps1: +cờ ms cho service (PathName under \Windows\). quickwin_winrs_inventory.go:
#       winrsInvHost +Prev/PrevTS (setHostData chuyển data cũ→prev); ExportWinRSInventory (csv 1 dòng/host
#       + json). router +route export. UI: checkbox showMicrosoft/onlyRunning (filteredServices/Tasks),
#       panel 'Changes since last scan' (diff data vs prev), nút Export CSV/JSON.
# SPEC: docs/L2-specs/core-patches/0027-inventory-filter-diff-export.md
# BASELINE: v2.18.16
#
